<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Online Voting Awareness Portal</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f8;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        nav {
            background-color: #34495e;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav a {
            background-color: #1abc9c;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 8px 14px;
            margin: 5px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #16a085;
        }

        marquee {
            background-color: #eaf2f8;
            padding: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            display: none;
        }

        input, select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #1abc9c;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>🗳️ Online Voting Awareness Portal</h1>
    <p>Supporting one party is good • Knowing your power is greater</p>
</header>

<marquee>📢 Your Vote is Your Voice | 🇮🇳 Vote Responsibly | 🔐 Secure Democracy</marquee>

<nav>
    <a href="#" onclick="showSection('about')">About</a>
    <a href="#" onclick="showSection('importance')">Importance</a>
    <a href="#" onclick="showSection('process')">Process</a>
    <a href="#" onclick="showSection('security')">Security</a>
    <a href="#" onclick="showSection('register')">Registration</a>
</nav>

<div class="container">

    <div class="card" id="about">
        <h2>📘 About Online Voting</h2>
        <p>
            Online voting allows citizens to cast their votes through secure digital platforms,
            improving accessibility and participation in elections.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" id="importance">
        <h2>⭐ Importance of Voting</h2>
        <p>
            Voting is a fundamental democratic right. It enables citizens to choose their leaders
            and actively participate in governance.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" id="process">
        <h2>🛠️ Online Voting Process</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Voter Registration</li>
            <li>Identity Verification</li>
            <li>Secure Authentication</li>
            <li>Vote Casting</li>
            <li>Confirmation</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="card" id="security">
        <h2>🔐 Security Measures</h2>
        <p>
            Strong encryption, authentication, and audit logs are used to ensure vote privacy
            and prevent fraud.
        </p>
        <meter value="0.9">90%</meter>
    </div>

    <!-- REGISTRATION SECTION -->
    <div class="card" id="register">
        <h2>📝 Voter Registration</h2>

        <form>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Full Name" required>
            <input type="email" placeholder="Email Address" required>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Voter ID Number" required>

            <select required>
                <option value="">Select State</option>
                <option>Tamil Nadu</option>
                <option>Karnataka</option>
                <option>Kerala</option>
                <option>Andhra Pradesh</option>
            </select>

            <button type="submit">Register</button>
        </form>
    </div>

</div>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Online Voting Awareness Portal</p>
    <p>Created by Harrish S</p>
</footer>

<script>
function showSection(id) {
    let sections = document.querySelectorAll(".card");
    sections.forEach(section => section.style.display = "none");
    document.getElementById(id).style.display = "block";
}

// default section
showSection("about");
</script>

</body>
</html>
